<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Special Offers | Flight Booking</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
 
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #f2f2f2);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
 
        .wrapper:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f0faff, #e0f7ff);
        }
 
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
 
        .offer-info {
            text-align: center;
            color: #555;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
 
        .benefits {
            text-align: left;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
 
        .steps {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
 
        .btn-container {
            text-align: center;
        }
 
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #2196f3;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
 
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0f6fca;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
 
        .btn::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 300%;
            height: 300%;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: -1;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(45deg);
        }
 
        .btn:hover::before {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
 
        /* Additional Wrappers */
        .wrapper-2 {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #fff, #f2f2f2);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
        }
 
        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
 
        .wrapper-2:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #f0faff, #e0f7ff);
        }
 
        .title-2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ff5722;
        }
 
        .content-2 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        li{
            list-style-type : none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="title">Special Offers</div>
        <div class="offer-info">Explore our current special offers and discounts for your next flight booking.</div>
        <div class="benefits">
            <div><strong>Benefits:</strong></div>
            <ul>
                <li>Discounted fares on selected routes.</li>
                <li>Extra baggage allowance for certain ticket types.</li>
                <li>Complimentary in-flight meals for business class bookings.</li>
                <li>Exclusive access to airport lounges for premium bookings.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="steps">Follow these simple steps to avail the offers:</div>
        <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="#" class="btn">Check Available Offers</a>
        </div>
    </div>
 
    <div class="wrapper-2">
        <div class="title-2">How to Avail Offers</div>
        <div class="content-2">
            <ol>
                <li>Visit our website and select your desired destination and travel dates.</li>
                <li>Choose the flights eligible for special offers.</li>
                <li>During checkout, apply the relevant promo code if applicable.</li>
                <li>Complete your booking and enjoy the benefits!</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
 
    <div class="wrapper-2">
        <div class="title-2">Best Time to Avail Offers</div>
        <div class="content-2">
            <p>Our special offers are limited-time deals. Book early to get the best prices and availability.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
 
    <div class="wrapper-2">
        <div class="title-2">Benefits of Availing Offers</div>
        <div class="content-2">
            <ul>
                <li>Save money with discounted fares.</li>
                <li>Enjoy additional perks like extra baggage allowance and in-flight meals.</li>
                <li>Access exclusive benefits for premium bookings.</li>
                <li>Flexible booking options with easy modifications and cancellations.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
 
    <div class="wrapper-2">
        <div class="title-2">Book Now for Exciting Offers!</div>
        <div class="content-2">
            <p>Don't miss out on our limited-time special offers. Book your flights today and experience travel at its best!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-container">
            <a href="#" class="btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>